version_description:
- New Google Parameters setting for users encountering repeated errors when fetching rankings.
- New Rebuild iCloud database feature for users with corrupted iCloud database.
- CAPTCHA image now works again. A recent change by Google broke it.

- Fixed graphical glitch for iPad users.
- Fixed an Export Report bug affecting some users.
- Included an option for comma or semi-colon delimiter when exporting rankings.
- PageRank has been discontinued by Google. The statistic has been removed from the app.
- Fixed a bug affecting Pro Pack subscribers. Please contact support if you were affected by the previous update.

- App now accepts longer emails when creating SEO Edge accounts.
- Fixed Alexa rank bug affecting some websites.

- Fixed a random crash caused by having too many keywords.
- Various minor bug fixes.
- Fix for CAPTCHA. Google now uses reCAPTCHA for human verification.
- Fixed a crash that occurs when exporting keywords from profiles with forward slashes in their domain names.

- Fixed Alexa and Backlinks statistics.
- Fixed CAPTCHA errors.
- Another attempt to fix the errors caused by changes on Google's end.

- Fixed the occasional errors when viewing list of competitors.
- Fixed occasional errors after verifying CAPTCHA.
